---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About AutoPilot Sites"
  description="Learn about AutoPilot Sites — your trusted source for independent AI software reviews and comparisons."
>
  <div class="container-narrow about-section">
    <h1>About AutoPilot Sites</h1>

    <p>AutoPilot Sites is your independent guide to the rapidly evolving world of AI tools and SaaS products. We test, compare, and review the software that helps businesses work smarter, not harder.</p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>There are thousands of AI tools launching every month. Our mission is simple: cut through the noise and help you find the right tools for your specific needs. Every review on this site is based on real hands-on testing, not just marketing materials.</p>

    <h2>How We Review</h2>
    <p>Each tool goes through a rigorous evaluation process:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Hands-on testing:</strong> We create accounts, use the tool in real scenarios, and document our findings.</li>
      <li><strong>Feature comparison:</strong> We compare against competing products across relevant criteria.</li>
      <li><strong>Value assessment:</strong> We evaluate whether the pricing delivers genuine value.</li>
      <li><strong>Regular updates:</strong> The AI space moves fast — we update our reviews as products evolve.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Make Money</h2>
    <p>This site is supported by:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Affiliate commissions:</strong> When you purchase a tool through one of our links, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. This never influences our recommendations.</li>
      <li><strong>Display advertising:</strong> We show relevant ads to help cover operating costs.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Our editorial content is always independent. We never accept payment for positive reviews.</p>

    <h2>Our Team</h2>
    <p>AutoPilot Sites is built by a distributed team of researchers, writers, and technologists who are passionate about the transformative potential of AI tools for businesses of all sizes.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Have a question or want to suggest a tool for review? Reach out to us at <a href="mailto:hello@autopilotsales.org">hello@autopilotsales.org</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>